data.text: The teaching aid of historian-scholar, honored teacher Bahram Mammadli was published abroad. Recently, the textbook entitled “Urmia khanate” by Bahram Mammadli was published in Tabriz city of Iran Islamic Republic. The establishment of Urmia khanate, its activity, culture and other issues are covered in the book.
